{"tid":2341800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本政府封國 宣布外國人由12月28日開始被禁入國","createTime":"2020-12-26T15:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T15:55:48.000Z","uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"84bb99e8f7b432f4ffc5b6a00b83241ddb8b5fb9","tid":2341800,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:46:21.000Z","msg":"日本政府封國 宣布外國人由12月28日開始被禁入國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wuhanpneumonia/foreigner-ban-entry/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwuhanpneumonia%2Fforeigner-ban-entry%2F&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUmrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=9a67ca58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/wuhanpneumonia/foreigner-ban-entry/</a><br />\n<br />\n根據日本傳媒讀賣新聞於26日晚上9年的報導，日本政府在12月26日宣布，因為新冠肺炎全世界的爆發，現將於12月28日開始，至2021年1月尾停止全世界的外國人入國。"},{"pid":"1fb78855a11cdc9298ae95a07aa569fe2f20f969","tid":2341800,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:47:47.000Z","msg":"變種病毒疫情爆發的英國與南非的入境雖然已經停止，但現在政府已把目標擴大到所有國家與地區。對於由海外歸來的日本國民，就需要在酒店或家中隔離14天。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府現時，除了某些國家之外，現已禁止由海外歸來的入境。但是，為了逐部緩和與世界的往來，政府由10月開始，逐部開放給留學生與工作者等持在留資格的外國人入國。但由於對於英國與南美，這個安排已於12月26日停止。而由於變種病毒已於這兩個國家以外的地方散播，因此決定暫停對全世界的例外入境安排。"},{"pid":"4d173375b07f5b4e57abbe0fe71d906889703db6","tid":2341800,"uid":55955,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:47:53.000Z","msg":"熱狗：恐懼撚，日本市民助長極權政府"},{"pid":"6500c60d3b4ed5879b6cba96018f89b192c969aa","tid":2341800,"uid":196961,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"84bb99e8f7b432f4ffc5b6a00b83241ddb8b5fb9","tid":2341800,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:46:21.000Z","msg":"日本政府封國 宣布外國人由12月28日開始被禁入國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wuhanpneumonia/foreigner-ban-entry/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwuhanpneumonia%2Fforeigner-ban-entry%2F&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUmrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=9a67ca58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/wuhanpneumonia/foreigner-ban-entry/</a><br />\n<br />\n根據日本傳媒讀賣新聞於26日晚上9年的報導，日本政府在12月26日宣布，因為新冠肺炎全世界的爆發，現將於12月28日開始，至2021年1月尾停止全世界的外國人入國。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xqNr7yH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxqNr7yH.jpg&h=b8a106e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇事啦，繼續開支那關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12594d2981342edce035010a111261a99511a15b","tid":2341800,"uid":38777,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:54:23.000Z","msg":"繼續奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce874900970ea8210be9dbff484522a03e528ea4","tid":2341800,"uid":161711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:55:48.000Z","msg":"東京奧運<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}